# eTape is a public, personal repo unrelated to SiteMinder — always resolve
# packages from the public registry here, regardless of any machine-level
# ~/.npmrc override (e.g. a corporate Artifactory mirror). Without this,
# `npm install`/`npm ci` on a machine with a private registry configured
# globally would bake that host into package-lock.json's "resolved" URLs,
# breaking installs anywhere else.
registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
